<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EMA522_06_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css">

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_06_su.css">

</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_06_su_0003">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-head="1">
                <div class="fraction-text-column" lang="y">
                    <div class="mixed_fraction ml_0">하준이는 조각보를 만드는 데 빨간색 천 한 장의
                        <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>5</span></span> 중에서 <span
                            class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>만큼을 사용했습니다. 조각보를 만드는 데 사용한 빨간색 천은
                        빨간색
                    </div>
                    <div>천 전체의 얼마인지 알아봅시다.</div>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <div class="input_area">
                <article class="page page_1">
                    <div class="img_row">

                        <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_06_SU/0002_img01.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                            <div class="flex dir_col f16r">
                                <div class="flex align_center dir_row gap_4">
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>5</span></span>
                                    <span>중에서 </span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>
                                    <span>만큼을</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>어떻게 구할 수 있을까?</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <h3 lang="y">구하는 식을 써 보세요.</h3>

                            <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap flex align_center">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="(1)/(5)xx(1)/(3)" text-align="center"
                                    placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                <!-- 분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2) -->
                                <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 -->
                                <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                                <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                                <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="page page_2">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        <span class="flex align_center gap_4">
                            <span>그림을 보고</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span>1</span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                            <span>&times;</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box">
                                <span>1</span>
                                <span>3</span>
                            </span>
                            <span>을 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.</span>
                        </span>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="question_box align_start dir_col">
                        <div class="flex">
                            <div class="reveal_wrap f32b">
                                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_06_SU/0003_img01.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                                <span class="abs_1" lang="y">
                                    <span class="fraction_box">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span>5</span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                <span class="abs_2" lang="y">
                                    <span class="fraction_box">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span>5</span>
                                    </span>
                                    <span>의</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span>3</span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                <span class="abs_3" lang="y">
                                    <span class="fraction_box gap_6">
                                        <span>1</span>
                                        <span class="flex gap_4">
                                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                                <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                                            </span>
                                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                                <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                            </span>
                                        </span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_center gap_4 m_auto">
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>&times;</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span>3</span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box gap_6">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span class="flex gap_4">
                                        <span class="input_wrap">
                                            <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="input_wrap">
                                            <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                        </span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <span class="fraction_box gap_6">
                                    <span>1</span>
                                    <span class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field data-answer-single="15"></math-field>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="page page_3">
                    <div class="img_row">

                        <div class="picture_wrap type2">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_06_SU/0002_img01.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                            <div class="flex dir_col f16r">
                                <div class="flex align_center dir_row gap_4">
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>5</span></span>
                                    <span>중에서 </span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>
                                    <span>만큼을</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>어떻게 구할 수 있을까?</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="input_area">
                            <h3 lang="y">구하는 식을 써 보세요.</h3>

                            <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap flex align_center">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="(1)/(15)" text-align="center"
                                    placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                <!-- 분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2) -->
                                <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 --> 
                                <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                                <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                                <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <!-- 예시 필드에서 사용 -->
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>